"And it is, it is
A glorious thing to be a pirate king"

20
00:01:28,301 --> 00:01:31,862
- Are you all right?
- As well as can be expected.

21
00:01:32,773 --> 00:01:34,673
If you want to cry, go ahead.

22
00:01:35,776 --> 00:01:38,074
I just hate this fucking tune.

23
