396
00:30:07,152 --> 00:30:08,380
Elizabeth!

397
00:30:11,523 --> 00:30:12,649
And you.

398
00:30:14,159 --> 00:30:15,683
You're looking good, Sister.

399
00:30:16,428 --> 00:30:17,861
That's because I am good.

400
