466
00:35:48,693 --> 00:35:50,388
You old softy.

467
00:35:52,697 --> 00:35:56,155
I can still get into this, you know,
size 14, short legs.

468
00:35:58,169 --> 00:35:59,966
Who was this little girl?

469
00:36:01,806 --> 00:36:03,637
