emotionally vulnerable.

657
00:47:00,231 --> 00:47:01,220
Well, yes.

658
00:47:01,532 --> 00:47:04,057
That being so,
Elizabeth should not be consorting...

659
00:47:04,135 --> 00:47:05,534
...with an aging Lothario.

660
00:47:05,836 --> 00:47:09,067
Even though he sends me flowers
two or three times a week.

661
00:47:09,273 --> 00:47:13,767
My concern is about you making
terrible fools of yourselves...

662
00:47:14,078 --> 00:47:16,273
...and of us at the school dance.

663
00:47:16,347 --> 00:47:18,338
Patrick will answer all the charges.

664
00:47:18,616 --> 00:47:22,450
- May I offer the case for the defense?
- Please. We're here to listen.

665
00:47:22,786 --> 00:47:23,650
Thank you.

666
00:47:24,054 --> 00:47:25,954
Well, I'll start with the easy bit.

667
00:47:26,023 --> 00:47:29,083
It's true that in the beginning,
I wore a pretty frock.

668
00:47:29,293 --> 00:47:33,491
And I played Run Rabbit Run
when I was one of those rabbits...

669
00:47:33,597 --> 00:47:35,690
...and I was running.

670
00:47:36,333 --> 00:47:40,429
