I did win some medals.

671
00:47:40,504 --> 00:47:41,630
You won medals?

672
00:47:41,705 --> 00:47:42,933
Can we see them?

673
00:47:46,377 --> 00:47:49,972
I always carry this one
as a good luck charm.

674
00:47:51,282 --> 00:47:55,116
