grandmother again after all these years.

675
00:47:55,352 --> 00:47:57,081
- Is it a good one?
- Yes, it is.

676
00:47:57,555 --> 00:47:58,852
It's a Military Cross.

677
00:47:59,123 --> 00:48:00,613
Seriously brilliant.

678
00:48:01,258 --> 00:48:02,782
But it's all irrelevant.

679
00:48:02,860 --> 00:48:05,829
What you have to understand
is that for six years...

680
00:48:06,530 --> 00:48:09,556
...we all lived with the possibility
that every second...

681
00:48:09,633 --> 00:48:11,191
...we could be killed.

682
00:48:13,337 --> 00:48:15,305
And that focuses the mind.

683
00:48:16,807 --> 00:48:19,674
It's frightening, yes, but it's also liberating.

