to my bloody credit card.

717
00:49:54,938 --> 00:49:55,927
Obviously.

718
00:49:56,006 --> 00:49:58,600
I'm not allowed one.
I only spent the money on you.

719
00:49:58,676 --> 00:50:01,236
- How did you get the number?
- I used my initiative.

720
00:50:01,912 --> 00:50:03,436
You looked in my handbag.

721
