you and wouldn't have been arrested.

1046
01:11:34,904 --> 01:11:37,930
And you wouldn't be going off
to almost certain death.

1047
01:11:47,316 --> 01:11:48,442
That was you?

1048
01:11:49,819 --> 01:11:51,377
Of course it was.

1049
01:11:52,989 --> 01:11:55,924
I've been wondering for years
who that little schoolgirl was.

1050
01:11:55,992 --> 01:11:58,517
Maybe not years,
but a good 20 minutes, certainly.

1051
01:11:58,928 --> 01:12:01,488
Shut up. Say something sensible for once.

1052
01:12:04,400 --> 01:12:05,628
Will you marry me?

1053
01:12:07,103 --> 01:12:08,434
Absolutely not.

1054
01:12:09,438 --> 01:12:12,305
