you gave me my first grown-up kiss.

1055
01:12:12,375 --> 01:12:16,141
- I'm not very good at remembering.
- I'm still waiting for the second.

1056
01:12:25,321 --> 01:12:27,949
Open Wound will be back
later this evening.

1057
01:12:31,193 --> 01:12:34,560
